fields.entry: Started broccoli, cauliflower, tomatoes, basil, chili peppers, bell peppers, shallots, scallions, leeks.
Potted up what I believe are broccoli and cauliflower. The labels got wet and smeared, so I don't know which is which, yet. Same issue with the cantaloupe.
Finished re-arranging raised beds to two 3-bed rows with more space between them to allow easier access. Still need to put down bark chips on the pathways.
